edu.xtec.jclic.clic3

Class Clic3Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.xtec.jclic.clic3.Clic3
      • edu.xtec.jclic.clic3.Clic3Activity

  • public class Clic3Activity
extends Clic3
    This class encapsulates the main properties of a Clic 3.0 activity, and provides methods to load it from a data stream and to convert it to a JClic Activity.
    Version:
    13.08.08
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
